202
00:16:00,370 --> 00:16:05,280
Director Kim sure is something else.

203
00:16:05,280 --> 00:16:08,090
What are you saying out of the blue?

204
00:16:08,090 --> 00:16:12,640
I was here late last night since I had a night counseling duty.

205
00:16:12,640 --> 00:16:15,250
He called me when I was about to leave.

206
00:16:16,580 --> 00:16:18,350
Did he?

207
00:16:18,350 --> 00:16:22,940
He told me to order a banner and gave me the copy.

208
00:16:22,940 --> 00:16:25,360
And he went out for a drink.

209
00:16:26,500 --> 00:16:29,700
When everyone else is jumping for joy,

210
00:16:29,700 --> 00:16:33,300
he was thinking that in his head.

211
00:16:33,300 --> 00:16:36,570
I found it strangely off-putting.

212
00:16:39,230 --> 00:16:42,210
Being a half step ahead of everyone else ...

213
00:16:42,210 --> 00:16:45,210
that's that guy's speciality!

214
00:16:45,210 --> 00:16:48,590
See how he established this place while other small academies were failing.

215
00:16:48,590 --> 00:16:53,020
Don't underestimate him just because he's mild-mannered.

216
00:16:53,020 --> 00:16:55,980
You'll have to learn from him.

217
00:16:57,440 --> 00:17:01,180
Gosh, it's not something you can learn.

218
00:17:01,180 --> 00:17:04,160
It's all about instinct.

219
00:17:04,160 --> 00:17:07,860
An old lady like me can't even imitate him.

220
00:17:08,950 --> 00:17:13,170
I scheduled the Huiwon class for just Wednesday nights for now.

221
00:17:13,170 --> 00:17:18,060
