240
00:18:38,370 --> 00:18:43,030
Is it too humble a lunch for a hero?

241
00:18:43,030 --> 00:18:44,870
It's okay.

242
00:18:46,050 --> 00:18:49,790
I wanted to treat you somewhere impressive,

243
00:18:49,790 --> 00:18:51,950
but I remembered this restaurant.

244
00:18:51,950 --> 00:18:56,780
