Let's eat.

259
00:20:21,820 --> 00:20:26,370
Is your younger brother still commuting from your parents' house?

260
00:20:26,370 --> 00:20:27,840
Yes.

261
00:20:29,270 --> 00:20:33,700
Sejong Government Complex must be far from there.

262
00:20:33,700 --> 00:20:36,720
He'll save up and get his own place soon.

263
00:20:36,720 --> 00:20:39,530
Time goes by so fast.

264
00:20:39,530 --> 00:20:42,040
It feels like yesterday when I paid his tuition.

265
00:20:42,040 --> 00:20:44,660
But he's a civil servant now.

266
00:20:55,410 --> 00:20:59,280
You must've heard everything from Jun Ho last night, right?

267
00:20:59,280 --> 00:21:00,850
Of course.

268
00:21:01,560 --> 00:21:06,020
It reminded me of the old days.

269
00:21:06,020 --> 00:21:07,980
I could tell.

270
00:21:07,980 --> 00:21:10,160
Thinking about it,

271
00:21:10,160 --> 00:21:16,630
it looks like Jun Ho has always been at turning points in our lives.

272
00:21:16,630 --> 00:21:18,420
Right.

273
00:21:20,590 --> 00:21:25,570
As I paid off the debt I created while making a film, thanks to you two

274
00:21:25,570 --> 00:21:29,180
and moved out of this building,

275
00:21:29,180 --> 00:21:32,840
I promised myself something.

276
00:21:33,600 --> 00:21:40,310
Never fail again, and never torment the people who trusted me again.

277
00:21:40,310 --> 00:21:43,830
That's one's duty as the leader.

278
00:21:46,720 --> 00:21:50,400
Since I was afraid to fail,

279
00:21:50,400 --> 00:21:54,480
I did something I shouldn't have done to you.

280
00:21:55,120 --> 00:21:57,790
I couldn't sleep thinking about the Gangbuk branch.

281
00:21:57,790 --> 00:22:00,970
A new area, unfamiliar schools,

282
00:22:00,970 --> 00:22:04,640
and the students outside of Daechi-dong.

283
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:08,220
I wondered how we could put our roots down there

284
00:22:08,220 --> 00:22:12,510
and who could achieve that for us.

285
00:22:12,510 --> 00:22:16,760
That's why I started feeling hasty.

286
00:22:16,760 --> 00:22:20,600
I was desperate to give you a major task

287
00:22:21,270 --> 00:22:23,600
that I forgot my initial spirit.

288
00:22:26,690 --> 00:22:30,080
You should get a TA.

289
00:22:30,080 --> 00:22:34,860
This would be independent of the TA you personally hired.

290
00:22:34,860 --> 00:22:39,420
The academy will be paying them instead.

291
00:22:39,420 --> 00:22:43,480
But I don't need one since I have fewer classes now.

292
00:22:44,500 --> 00:22:49,490
I sincerely apologize as the director.

293
00:22:49,490 --> 00:22:52,900
Please teach Chanyeong High's 11th-grade class again.

294
00:22:54,850 --> 00:22:56,320
Cheers.

295
00:22:58,990 --> 00:23:02,100
 I felt so guilty, I thought I'd die. 

296
00:23:02,100 --> 00:23:04,620
- Director.
 - Yes?

297
00:23:04,620 --> 00:23:07,380
That's not how you apologize.

298
00:23:07,380 --> 00:23:09,940
Why are you embarrassing me, too?

299
00:23:11,620 --> 00:23:13,440
Well, you know,

300
00:23:13,440 --> 00:23:18,030
if you're embarrassed in front of Mr. Lee and Ms. Nam, don't worry.

301
00:23:18,030 --> 00:23:22,770
Jun Ho needs to be focusing on Huiwon High

302
00:23:22,770 --> 00:23:27,640
and Ms. Nam will be given an appropriate class.

303
00:23:27,640 --> 00:23:34,450
Indeed, you need to keep the Daechi-dong branch steady as a rock

304
00:23:34,450 --> 00:23:39,480
so our academy can grow. I finally realized that now.

305
00:23:39,480 --> 00:23:42,500
I understand you feel disappointed.

306
00:23:42,500 --> 00:23:46,010
I-If my... I'm stuttering now.

307
00:23:46,010 --> 00:23:48,580
If my apology wasn't enough, let me once again—

308
00:23:48,580 --> 00:23:50,310
I'm not saying it wasn't enough.

309
00:23:50,310 --> 00:23:53,090
I'm saying it was wrong.

310
00:23:55,710 --> 00:23:57,470
Am I hard to understand?

311
00:23:57,470 --> 00:24:00,600
I'm known for easily explaining things.

312
00:24:00,600 --> 00:24:04,050
Seriously. Team Leader Seo.

313
00:24:07,100 --> 00:24:08,960
Come on, Seo Hye Jin—

314
00:24:08,960 --> 00:24:13,630
You didn't just cancel my Chanyeong class. You broke our trust.

315
00:24:13,630 --> 00:24:17,500
Don't be like that. That's not right. Don't exaggerate.

316
00:24:17,500 --> 00:24:23,830
I know that you and Assistant Director have been nervous for about five years.

317
00:24:30,570 --> 00:24:32,070
Yes.

318
00:24:32,760 --> 00:24:35,140
Yes, this is Seo Hye Jin.

319
00:24:39,000 --> 00:24:40,560
Yes.

320
00:24:41,210 --> 00:24:44,260
But how... yes...

321
00:24:44,260 --> 00:24:46,360
How did you get my number?

322
00:24:48,250 --> 00:24:51,790
Yes, I've heard of them.

323
00:24:56,210 --> 00:24:58,290
No, I'm not interested in seeing them.

324
00:24:58,290 --> 00:25:00,670
Even a fool would've noticed.

325
00:25:00,670 --> 00:25:02,180
Whenever I got a call from a different academy,

326
00:25:02,180 --> 00:25:07,440
you brought up our old friendship and loyalty.

327
00:25:07,440 --> 00:25:08,950
But it didn't matter to me.

328
00:25:08,950 --> 00:25:11,960
I thought maybe I didn't provide enough trust.

329
00:25:11,960 --> 00:25:15,970
So, I signed your contracts, no matter what they said.

330
00:25:15,970 --> 00:25:19,640
The more I read this clause, the more I hate it.

331
00:25:19,640 --> 00:25:24,820
You can't get a job in the area for a year if you quit your job.

332
00:25:24,820 --> 00:25:26,500
It doesn't happen all the time,

333
00:25:26,500 --> 00:25:29,190
but you might have to compensate them for the loss.

334
00:25:29,190 --> 00:25:30,680
You know that, right?

335
00:25:30,680 --> 00:25:32,240
It doesn't matter since I won't quit.

336
00:25:32,240 --> 00:25:35,040
I'll sign if everything else looks fine.

337
00:25:35,720 --> 00:25:39,770
 I never even jaywalked after my face started appearing in ads in Daechi-dong. 

338
00:25:39,770 --> 00:25:42,960
And I never swore so I wouldn't damage the academy's image.

339
00:25:42,960 --> 00:25:44,920
- Team Leader Seo.
 - Yes.

340
00:25:44,920 --> 00:25:46,510
It was because I was grateful.

341
00:25:46,510 --> 00:25:49,230
Because you helped me when I was struggling.

342
00:25:49,230 --> 00:25:51,550
But I didn't receive anything for free.

343
00:25:51,550 --> 00:25:54,510
My brother's tuition and my father's hospital bill?

344
00:25:54,510 --> 00:25:57,640
It was an advance. You never gave it to me for free.

345
00:25:57,640 --> 00:26:00,170
Why do you talk as if it were a charity case?

346
00:26:00,170 --> 00:26:03,020
I must've caused a miscommunication.

347
00:26:03,020 --> 00:26:05,320
I was disappointed in you when you docked my pay,

348
00:26:05,320 --> 00:26:09,930
but I thought our relationship was still good enough.

349
00:26:10,790 --> 00:26:13,970
You said Seo Hye Jin is more important than a few students.

350
00:26:13,970 --> 00:26:16,360
I believed it when you said that.

351
00:26:18,650 --> 00:26:21,300
I felt rewarded seeing the academy grow, too.

352
00:26:21,300 --> 00:26:25,050
But you must've thought all of that was yours.

353
00:26:25,050 --> 00:26:27,420
Gosh, seriously.

354
00:26:28,160 --> 00:26:30,690
Don't act all high and mighty.

355
00:26:30,690 --> 00:26:33,120
You wanted to be the youngest director at the Gangbuk branch.

356
00:26:33,120 --> 00:26:34,850
I'm glad you brought that up.

357
00:26:34,850 --> 00:26:36,620
Is the Gangbuk branch mine?

358
00:26:36,620 --> 00:26:38,170
Should I grow it and keep it?

359
00:26:38,170 --> 00:26:39,770
It's because I was scared!

360
00:26:39,770 --> 00:26:41,890
Director Kim Hyeon Tak!

361
00:26:41,890 --> 00:26:44,450
Can't you be more honest?

362
00:26:44,450 --> 00:26:46,430
I'm not lying.

363
00:26:47,720 --> 00:26:50,110
What did you say?

364
00:26:50,110 --> 00:26:52,450
I really was scared.

365
00:26:54,910 --> 00:27:00,240
I have nightmares where you take the entire Chaneyong High with you.

366
00:27:00,240 --> 00:27:02,590
You were shoveling my money away, too.

367
00:27:02,590 --> 00:27:05,580
That's my reward for working 15 hours a day without taking weekends off.

368
00:27:05,580 --> 00:27:08,490
How did you end up this way, Director?

369
00:27:08,490 --> 00:27:10,620
Ask a hundred directors on the streets.

370
00:27:10,620 --> 00:27:12,420
Ask them if they're afraid of teachers like you.

371
00:27:12,420 --> 00:27:14,230
I didn't change.

372
00:27:14,230 --> 00:27:15,990
I just became a director.

373
00:27:15,990 --> 00:27:18,010
You said you were different than other directors!

374
00:27:18,010 --> 00:27:20,300
See? You never lose an argument!

375
00:27:20,300 --> 00:27:23,520
Gosh, fight outside!

376
00:27:31,870 --> 00:27:35,280
I wanted us to have a beautiful goodbye someday

377
00:27:36,470 --> 00:27:38,510
if my time to part with you came.

378
00:27:38,510 --> 00:27:41,400
Gosh, I said I-I was sorry.

379
00:27:41,400 --> 00:27:44,020
Why would you say something so awful?

380
00:27:44,020 --> 00:27:47,450
Give the Chanyeong High 11th-grade class to Ms. Nam and Mr. Lee.

381
00:27:47,450 --> 00:27:50,750
They're working hard on it.

382
00:27:51,770 --> 00:27:53,280
Wait...

383
00:27:59,520 --> 00:28:01,340
Darn it.

384
00:28:01,340 --> 00:28:05,940
 Teachers' Office 

385
00:28:05,940 --> 00:28:11,270
 Students are not allowed to enter while the final exams are being taken. 

386
00:28:11,270 --> 00:28:14,390
You teach the 11th grade.

387
00:28:14,390 --> 00:28:19,290
I'm asking why you're involving yourself in the 10th-grade exam.

388
00:28:20,930 --> 00:28:26,060
I've created 10th-grade exams for three years until last year.

389
00:28:26,060 --> 00:28:30,840
You can apply the school's exam trends or overall direction, too.

390
00:28:32,320 --> 00:28:34,990
I assume you didn't do that as a hobby.

391
00:28:34,990 --> 00:28:38,160
You don't even have a 10th-grade class.

392
00:28:38,160 --> 00:28:42,050
The head of the 10th grade requested this.

393
00:28:43,820 --> 00:28:48,290
We'd feel better if you had another look.

394
00:28:50,500 --> 00:28:52,690
- Feel better?
 - I'm not...

395
00:28:52,690 --> 00:28:56,820
I'm not necessarily telling you to use the old exams.

396
00:29:00,510 --> 00:29:02,690
I appreciate the gesture.

397
00:29:08,660 --> 00:29:11,120
He's so stubborn.

398
00:29:14,070 --> 00:29:18,610
I'll take any kind of cigarettes. A lighter, too.

399
00:29:18,610 --> 00:29:21,070
We don't sell cigarettes.

400
00:29:21,990 --> 00:29:24,530
The parents complained about it.

401
00:29:28,200 --> 00:29:31,990
 Mr. Pyo is such a troublemaker. 

402
00:29:35,620 --> 00:29:38,110
Okay, then. Get back to work.

403
00:29:38,110 --> 00:29:39,530
Okay.

404
00:30:24,460 --> 00:30:28,280
Can I bum a cigarette from you?

405
00:30:28,280 --> 00:30:32,500
I quit a long time ago.

406
00:30:36,000 --> 00:30:38,300
Okay. Here you go.

407
00:31:35,190 --> 00:31:40,470
 Prepare for school exams and college entrance exam with Daechi Chase 

408
00:31:50,590 --> 00:31:55,120
So Yeong, you finished reading the contract I gave you, right?

409
00:31:57,300 --> 00:31:58,860
We'll be counting on you, then.

410
00:31:58,860 --> 00:32:01,320
Yes. Tell Jae Yeong to stop by sometime.

411
00:32:01,320 --> 00:32:02,530
Thank you in advance.

412
00:32:02,530 --> 00:32:04,240
I'll do my best to teach them.

413
00:32:04,240 --> 00:32:06,850
Get home safely.

414
00:32:13,480 --> 00:32:16,010
How come you don't even get nervous?

415
00:32:16,910 --> 00:32:18,920
There's no time for that.

416
00:32:20,420 --> 00:32:22,580
Would you like some tea?

417
00:32:22,580 --> 00:32:23,940
Sure.

418
00:32:26,650 --> 00:32:31,620
The mothers sometimes bring nice teas.

419
00:32:31,620 --> 00:32:35,000
Of course, only when their kids' grades improve.

420
00:32:35,000 --> 00:32:37,540
If the grades go down,

421
00:32:38,480 --> 00:32:41,850
they swear instead of gifting teas.

422
00:32:44,120 --> 00:32:47,810
- Thank you.
 - It tastes pretty good.

423
00:32:51,150 --> 00:32:55,800
They have expensive taste since they're mothers who live in Gangnam.

424
00:32:58,100 --> 00:33:02,450
You talk as if you aren't one of them.

425
00:33:02,450 --> 00:33:04,900
My gosh.

426
00:33:05,920 --> 00:33:09,560
By the way, I'm not sure

427
00:33:09,560 --> 00:33:13,140
if I can be so casual with you.

428
00:33:13,140 --> 00:33:17,430
You became the most desired teacher at the academy.

429
00:33:18,200 --> 00:33:19,910
Please, keep it casual.

430
00:33:19,910 --> 00:33:22,590
- Thank you. 
 - Not at all

431
00:33:28,830 --> 00:33:34,180
It's such a cruel world, isn't it?

432
00:33:37,270 --> 00:33:38,870
Well...

433
00:33:39,670 --> 00:33:45,140
I've been working at the academy for five or six years already.

434
00:33:45,140 --> 00:33:49,270
Things are so different than how they seem outside.

435
00:33:49,270 --> 00:33:54,790
The teachers must feel so lonely.

436
00:33:54,790 --> 00:33:58,120
They don't have anyone to rely on

437
00:33:58,120 --> 00:34:00,860
or to trust.

438
00:34:06,670 --> 00:34:13,290
Team Leader Seo is very hurt by this, right?

439
00:34:14,470 --> 00:34:16,210
Yes.

440
00:34:16,210 --> 00:34:20,280
I don't know entirely, but probably quite a bit.

441
00:34:20,280 --> 00:34:22,790
Of course, she is.

442
00:34:22,790 --> 00:34:26,540
When they said they'd give the Chanyeong class to someone else,

443
00:34:26,540 --> 00:34:30,420
even my heart sank.

444
00:34:36,450 --> 00:34:39,800
Will she renew the contract?

445
00:34:42,620 --> 00:34:45,570
I'm not sure. I don't know that much, either.

446
00:34:45,570 --> 00:34:48,370
Should I ask her myself?

447
00:34:48,370 --> 00:34:50,880
No, come on.

448
00:34:50,880 --> 00:34:53,330
I wasn't asking that.

449
00:34:59,940 --> 00:35:07,040
Ms. Seo first joined the academy when she was barely 20.

450
00:35:07,040 --> 00:35:11,450
She was such a baby if you think about it.

451
00:35:12,490 --> 00:35:16,940
When I had a counseling session with her because of your mom's recommendation,

452
00:35:16,940 --> 00:35:20,690
I couldn't even call her "Teacher."

453
00:35:22,010 --> 00:35:23,370
I felt that way, too.

454
00:35:23,370 --> 00:35:25,080
Right?

455
00:35:26,440 --> 00:35:30,650
But how many years has it been?

456
00:35:30,650 --> 00:35:36,180
She's been so devoted to the academy for over a decade.

457
00:35:37,020 --> 00:35:41,880
She's not calculating at all because of that.

458
00:35:41,880 --> 00:35:44,990
She never got to enjoy life, either.

459
00:35:45,790 --> 00:35:47,740
You're right.

460
00:35:47,740 --> 00:35:52,200
Someone like that can get scary

461
00:35:52,200 --> 00:35:55,920
once they change their mind.

462
00:35:58,130 --> 00:36:00,920
Aren't you going to go independent, ma'am?

463
00:36:00,920 --> 00:36:02,290
What?

464
00:36:02,290 --> 00:36:04,070
Seung Gyu told me.

465
00:36:04,070 --> 00:36:09,580
That you're planning to start an academy with a director if your husband approves.

466
00:36:12,490 --> 00:36:14,670
My goodness.

467
00:36:16,840 --> 00:36:21,190
Seriously, this is how sons are.

468
00:36:23,330 --> 00:36:26,410
Why doesn't he understand his mother?

469
00:36:29,210 --> 00:36:34,700
It's not my husband's approval I'm waiting for.

470
00:36:35,590 --> 00:36:38,480
It's a capable director.

471
00:36:42,100 --> 00:36:45,660
It'd have to be a serious talent to satisfy you.

472
00:36:45,660 --> 00:36:47,870
Of course.

473
00:36:47,870 --> 00:36:49,920
They'd have to be...

474
00:36:50,620 --> 00:36:56,510
at least as good as Ms. Seo to satisfy me.

475
00:37:07,030 --> 00:37:09,640
Seo Hye Jin is so popular.

476
00:37:12,930 --> 00:37:15,130
Mr. Lee.

477
00:37:15,130 --> 00:37:16,880
You're a busy man today.

478
00:37:16,880 --> 00:37:18,520
I thought the counseling session ended a while ago.

479
00:37:18,520 --> 00:37:20,620
Where have you been?

480
00:37:20,620 --> 00:37:22,670
- Were you looking for me?
 - Of course.

481
00:37:22,670 --> 00:37:24,570
Do you have time to loaf around?

482
00:37:24,570 --> 00:37:26,520
I wasn't loafing around.

483
00:37:26,520 --> 00:37:28,800
I'll be in the office.

484
00:37:31,090 --> 00:37:32,580
Let's go to the reference room.

485
00:37:32,580 --> 00:37:35,050
We need to create class material for Huiwon High.

486
00:37:35,050 --> 00:37:37,990
I'll create my part myself. Just review it for me.

487
00:37:37,990 --> 00:37:39,690
I know you're busy.

488
00:37:40,280 --> 00:37:42,670
Even if Si Wu brought all of his friends,

489
00:37:42,670 --> 00:37:45,670
we'd barely meet the minimum enrollment requirement.

490
00:37:45,670 --> 00:37:49,410
Student care is critical with small classes. There's still a lot you don't know.

491
00:37:49,410 --> 00:37:52,340
I'll ask you questions if I have any.

492
00:37:59,770 --> 00:38:02,090
I said I could do a good job.

493
00:38:12,160 --> 00:38:13,800
Have a seat.

494
00:38:21,790 --> 00:38:23,480
Jun Ho,

495
00:38:24,750 --> 00:38:27,160
should I share my trade secret with you?

496
00:38:27,780 --> 00:38:31,670
It's okay. You said it'd be unfair for other teachers.

497
00:38:31,670 --> 00:38:34,580
No, you'll find out about it soon, too.

498
00:38:37,830 --> 00:38:40,970
Once you start teaching students,

499
00:38:40,970 --> 00:38:43,370
you'll have a favorite eventually.

500
00:38:43,940 --> 00:38:46,680
Si Wu will be like that to you.

501
00:38:49,540 --> 00:38:52,380
You were my favorite.

502
00:38:52,380 --> 00:38:56,890
Seung Gyu, Ho Jae, and Tae Hyeon were all great,

503
00:38:59,610 --> 00:39:01,700
but I liked you the most.

504
00:39:01,700 --> 00:39:04,220
Don't tell Manager Kim.

505
00:39:04,220 --> 00:39:08,360
It's because my grades improved the most

506
00:39:08,360 --> 00:39:10,480
and I brought a lot of my friends, too.

507
00:39:10,480 --> 00:39:15,480
Yes. I thought that was why, too, but no.

508
00:39:15,480 --> 00:39:20,570
Even if your grades went down and the friends you brought quit,

509
00:39:20,570 --> 00:39:22,570
you...

510
00:39:23,670 --> 00:39:26,050
were very precious as you were.

511
00:39:27,720 --> 00:39:30,780
I guess I wanted to do more for you because of that.

512
00:39:30,780 --> 00:39:33,820
So, I said some silly things yesterday.

513
00:39:33,820 --> 00:39:35,980
I said I was disappointed and stuff.

514
00:39:38,130 --> 00:39:40,560
Forget about things like that.

515
00:39:40,560 --> 00:39:43,820
Forget about feeling grateful, guilty, and disappointed.

516
00:39:43,820 --> 00:39:45,990
Just focus on your goal.

517
00:39:45,990 --> 00:39:49,930
I'll help you as much as I can if you need anything.

518
00:39:55,390 --> 00:40:00,450
I went in front of your house after we parted last night.

519
00:40:38,750 --> 00:40:41,220
There's something you don't know.

520
00:40:42,540 --> 00:40:43,810
What is it?

521
00:40:43,810 --> 00:40:46,840
More than you think,

522
