I can understand that.

796
01:01:22,330 --> 01:01:23,910
But...

797
01:01:25,320 --> 01:01:29,430
I respected him today. Although it was just a tiny bit.

798
01:01:29,430 --> 01:01:32,080
Even though he got you into this mess?

799
01:01:32,080 --> 01:01:35,080
I didn't think he'd kneel down.

800
01:01:35,980 --> 01:01:41,110
I thought he'd make ridiculous excuses like last time, but, really...

801
01:01:41,790 --> 01:01:43,970
It was a shock.

802
01:01:45,630 --> 01:01:47,870
I thought, "You have to do that much

803
01:01:48,640 --> 01:01:51,930
to get what you want."

804
01:01:51,930 --> 01:01:54,890
Yes, he can be slimy

805
01:01:54,890 --> 01:01:57,690
and cunning sometimes.

806
01:01:57,690 --> 01:02:02,350
He acts like a child sometimes, as he did today.

807
01:02:02,350 --> 01:02:05,580
What kind of child drinks like he did?

808
01:02:05,580 --> 01:02:07,300
You're right.

809
01:02:17,940 --> 01:02:19,490
Ms. Seo,

810
01:02:21,290 --> 01:02:24,080
do you want to go back to the old days?

811
01:02:25,090 --> 01:02:27,010
Before I came here.

812
01:02:27,010 --> 01:02:29,690
Back when everything was predictable?

813
01:02:34,680 --> 01:02:35,950
That's the plan.

814
01:02:35,950 --> 01:02:39,240
I'm not asking about your plan. I'm asking how you feel.

815
01:02:40,120 --> 01:02:49,060


816
01:02:51,450 --> 01:02:54,700
I promised I wouldn't hold you back.

817
01:02:54,700 --> 01:02:57,880
It's ridiculous for me to say this,

818
01:02:57,880 --> 01:03:01,090
but Director Kim gave me courage.

819
01:03:01,090 --> 01:03:04,390
Either by kneeling down or embarrassing myself,

820
01:03:04,390 --> 01:03:06,570
I need to say what I need to say.

821
01:03:10,090 --> 01:03:14,330
You said you'd get me anything I want or need.

822
01:03:16,620 --> 01:03:19,020
I need you, Ms. Seo.

823
01:03:21,720 --> 01:03:23,420
You said to leave while you were letting me go.

824
01:03:23,420 --> 01:03:26,090
I'm not talking about Choeseon Korean.

825
01:03:32,930 --> 01:03:38,620
Tell me now if you want to go back to before I came here.

826
01:03:38,620 --> 01:03:41,460
I'll try my best to restrain myself once more.

827
01:03:55,730 --> 01:03:58,690
If you aren't asking what my plan is,

828
01:04:09,730 --> 01:04:12,260
I don't really want to go back.

829
01:04:24,290 --> 01:04:26,240
You knew, right?

830
01:04:28,750 --> 01:04:30,690
Knew what?

831
01:04:30,690 --> 01:04:32,940
How you really feel.

832
01:04:35,620 --> 01:04:37,640
And how I feel, too.

833
01:04:41,020 --> 01:04:44,500
No matter how much I think about it, there's no way you didn't notice ...

834
01:04:47,090 --> 01:04:49,590
that Lee Jun Ho's first love was

835
01:04:50,780 --> 01:04:52,790
Seo Hye Jin.

836
01:04:55,710 --> 01:04:57,320
What are you talking about?

837
01:04:57,320 --> 01:04:59,070
And...

838
01:05:00,110 --> 01:05:03,570
I can no longer just dismiss it as first love.

839
01:05:08,540 --> 01:05:13,010
My feelings keep spilling over because they keep growing.

840
01:05:15,430 --> 01:05:20,450
♫  Love was my greatest teacher  ♫

841
01:05:20,450 --> 01:05:24,030
♫  I knew it then  ♫

842
01:05:27,010 --> 01:05:31,000
♫  I know it now  ♫

843
01:05:31,000 --> 01:05:35,210
♫  For once in my life  ♫

844
01:05:35,210 --> 01:05:42,290
♫  I think I'm finally going to make it right  ♫

845
01:05:42,290 --> 01:05:50,800
♫  Years ago I let you pass me by,  but now's our time  ♫

846
01:05:50,800 --> 01:06:01,500
♫  You walked in my door, and the love I had for you before  ♫

847
01:06:01,500 --> 01:06:09,670
♫  Came shining through just like a star above the cloud  ♫

848
01:06:09,670 --> 01:06:20,440
♫  I knew it then, I know it now  ♫

849
01:06:24,530 --> 01:06:29,660
♫  It's in your eyes as they move  ♫

850
01:06:31,100 --> 01:06:37,530
♫  It's how you call my name out loud  ♫

851
01:06:37,530 --> 01:06:42,660
♫  There's some kind of music in you  ♫

852
01:06:42,660 --> 01:06:46,560
♫  I knew it then  ♫

