01:06:49,410 --> 01:06:53,490
 The Midnight Romance in Hagwon 

854
01:06:53,490 --> 01:06:55,030
 I just told you how I feel. 

855
01:06:55,030 --> 01:06:57,390
 - You're crazy.
 - I like you. 

856
01:06:57,390 --> 01:06:59,020
 Please think of me as a man. 

857
01:06:59,020 --> 01:07:00,240
 - By chance, is this—
 - No. 

858
01:07:00,240 --> 01:07:03,320
 Breaking news. Seo Hye Jin might quit. 

859
01:07:03,320 --> 01:07:06,200
 She can't refuse. The conditions are perfect. 

860
01:07:06,200 --> 01:07:08,140
 I won't tell anyone what I saw today. 

861
01:07:08,140 --> 01:07:11,930
 You can't get everything you want by bringing up first love. 

862
01:07:11,930 --> 01:07:14,500
 Just remember that I like you. 

863
01:07:14,500 --> 01:07:17,180
 All I can see is Seo Hye Jin. 

864
01:07:17,180 --> 01:07:19,180
 You're so cheeky. 

865
01:07:19,180 --> 01:07:22,380
 I do almost everything I set my mind to. You know, right? 

